TUI grows to 10+ distinct screens.\n\nSources:\n- [rat-salsa on GitHub](https://github.com/thscharler/rat-salsa)\n- [rat-salsa on crates.io](https://crates.io/crates/rat-salsa)\n- [tui-realm on GitHub](https://github.com/veeso/tui-realm)\n- [tui-realm on crates.io](https://crates.io/crates/tuirealm)\n- [tui-react on lib.rs](https://lib.rs/crates/tui-react)\n- [Byron/tui-crates StatefulWidget discussion](https://github.com/Byron/tui-crates/discussions/9)\n- [ratatui-interact on GitHub](https://github.com/Brainwires/ratatui-interact)\n- [widgetui on GitHub](https://github.com/TheEmeraldBee/widgetui)\n- [awesome-ratatui](https://github.com/ratatui/awesome-ratatui)</result>\n<usage><total_tokens>39860</total_tokens><tool_uses>21</tool_uses><duration_ms>188848</duration_ms></usage>\n</task-notification>\nFull transcript available at: /tmp/claude-1000/-home-leon0399-Projects-reme/cde6fd4c-88a8-464b-941a-e71717209706/tasks/a638421d319e3b680.output",
