n #5. Pattern from iamb's `Requester` / `WorkerTask`.\n\n## Acceptance criteria\n\n- [ ] All `tokio::spawn` + `action_tx` patterns go through `BackendHandle`\n- [ ] `BackendHandle` is testable (can verify action sent without real network)\n- [ ] `cargo test` and `cargo clippy` pass\nEOF\n)\" 2>&1",
